# The Spider — the first Animate demo story.
# Edit this file and save: the page reloads with your changes.

title: The Spider
scene: park

LIN walks in from left
LIN (happy): What a beautiful day!

LIN sits

MAX runs in from right
MAX (scared): There's a spider on the bench!!
screen shakes

LIN jumps
LIN trembles

MAX laughs
MAX: Ha! Just kidding.

camera zooms on LIN
LIN (angry) shakes head
LIN: That was NOT funny, Max!
camera resets

MAX (confused): Okay, okay... sorry!
MAX points
MAX (scared): Wait... is THAT a spider?!

LIN (surprised) jumps
LIN trembles
MAX trembles

wait 1s

LIN (laughing): Now we're even!
MAX falls
MAX (laughing): Good one!

MAX stands
LIN waves
LIN walks out
MAX (happy): See you tomorrow!
MAX runs out
